meta {
  name: Connect - White Player (GameStateSync)
  type: ws
  seq: 2
}

ws {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/ws/game/{{gameId}}?token={{whiteToken}}
  auth: inherit
}

docs {
  # Connexion White Player — réception du GameStateSync

  Se connecte au WebSocket de la partie en tant que joueur blanc.

  **Messages reçus automatiquement du serveur :**
  1. `GameAuthSuccess` — authentification réussie
  2. `GameStateSync` — état complet de la partie :
     ```json
     {
       "type": "GameStateSync",
       "gameId": "...",
       "positionFen": "rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1",
       "moveHistory": [],
       "gameStatus": "IN_PROGRESS",
       "currentSide": "WHITE",
       "whitePlayerId": "...",
       "blackPlayerId": "...",
       "whiteUsername": "alice",
       "blackUsername": "bob"
     }
     ```
}
